\
### Flow 3 \'97 OCR Extraction\
\
**Use for:** Extracting raw text from documents or images. Pass a publicly accessible file URL. The model returns the full extracted text, preserving structure.\
\
```\
Flow ID:   2b8fd71b-b101-4001-8660-4d3bedfc1f10\
Session:   Not used \'97 omit sessionId\
Inputs:    4\
```\
\
| # | inputId | Purpose |\
|---|---------|---------|\
| 1 | `varInputNode_1773364131277_0.8862` | Extraction instruction (usually a short prompt) |\
| 2 | `varInputNode_1773434271666_0.6770` | **Full public URL of the file to extract** |\
| 3 | `varInputNode_1773434287086_0.5082` | Model parameters |\
| 4 | `varInputNode_1773434416738_0.6139` | System prompt |\
\
**Full example body:**\
\
```json\
\{\
  "variableInputs": [\
    \{\
      "inputId": "varInputNode_1773364131277_0.8862",\
      "inputText": "Extract all text from this document."\
    \},\
    \{\
      "inputId": "varInputNode_1773434271666_0.6770",\
      "inputText": "https://yourdomain.com/uploads/court-filing.pdf"\
    \},\
    \{\
      "inputId": "varInputNode_1773434287086_0.5082",\
      "inputText": "\\"temperature\\": 0.2, \\"max_tokens\\": 20000"\
    \},\
    \{\
      "inputId": "varInputNode_1773434416738_0.6139",\
      "inputText": "You are a precise document OCR extraction agent. Extract all text from the provided document or image faithfully and completely. Preserve the original structure, headings, paragraphs, lists, and tables as closely as possible. Do not summarize, interpret, or add commentary \'97 return only the extracted text."\
    \}\
  ]\
\}\
```\
\
**Recommended system prompt for OCR:**\
> You are a precise document OCR extraction agent. Extract all text from the provided document or image faithfully and completely. Preserve the original structure, headings, paragraphs, lists, and tables as closely as possible. Do not summarize, interpret, or add commentary \'97 return only the extracted text.\
\
**Recommended temperature:** `0.2` (low, for faithful extraction)  \
**Recommended max_tokens:** `20000` (documents can be long)\
\
