\
## Model Parameters Format\
\
The model parameters input is **not** a JSON object \'97 it is a raw string containing JSON key-value pairs (without the surrounding `\{\}`). The flow injects this directly into a larger parameter structure.\
\
**Chat model (Flow 1):**\
```\
  "temperature": 0.3,\
  "max_tokens": 10024,\
  "chat_template_kwargs": \{\
        "enable_thinking": false\
      \},\
  "thinking_token_budget": 1028\
```\
\
**General model (Flow 2):**\
```\
  "temperature": 0.3,\
  "max_tokens": 8024,\
  "chat_template_kwargs": \{\
        "enable_thinking": false\
      \}\
```\
\
**OCR model (Flow 3):**\
```\
"temperature": 0.2, "max_tokens": 20000\
```\
\
To enable chain-of-thought reasoning (Flow 1 only):\
```\
"enable_thinking": true\
"thinking_token_budget": 1028   
\f1 \uc0\u8592 
\f0  controls how many tokens the model uses for internal reasoning\
```\
\
**Recommended temperature ranges:**\
- `0.2\'960.3` for extraction, classification, deterministic tasks\
- `0.5\'960.7` for analysis, summarization\
- `0.7\'961.0` for creative or open-ended tasks\
\
