\
## Checklist Before First Call\
\
- [ ] API key stored in env variable, read at runtime (not hardcoded)\
- [ ] `api-key` header set (not `Authorization`, not `Bearer`)\
- [ ] Correct flow ID for the task\
- [ ] All required inputs present with exact `inputId` strings\
- [ ] Image URLs are absolute public HTTPS URLs\
- [ ] Model parameters sent as a raw JSON fragment string (not a JSON object)\
- [ ] Timeout set to 600,000ms (10 minutes)\
- [ ] Response parsed via the defensive `extractResponseText` function\
- [ ] Disclaimer stripped from response text before display\
- [ ] Document context does not say "No documents in session." when no docs are loaded\
}